<p>The forked top of this walnut shaft resembles a combination of a <Link to="/eq-misc/dowsing_rod">dowsing rod</Link> and the curled horns of a beast, and a delicate gemstone hovers between its enfolding arms. The staff allows use of the following spells:</p>
