ff:_spherewalkers_staff,staff_of_curses:_staff_of_curses,staff_of_the_dark_tapestry:_staff_of_the_dark_tapestry,staff_of_fortune:_staff_of_fortune,staff_of_dark_flame:_staff_of_dark_flame,staff_of_performance:_staff_of_performance,animate_staff:_animate_staff,staff_of_hunting:_staff_of_hunting,staff_of_revelations:_staff_of_revelations,staff_of_illumination:_staff_of_illumination,staff_of_the_freed_man:_staff_of_the_freed_man,doomsday_staff:_doomsday_staff,staff_of_obstacles:_staff_of_obstacles,staff_of_heaven_and_earth:_staff_of_heaven_and_earth,staff_of_travel:_staff_of_travel,staff_of_hoarding:_staff_of_hoarding,crook_of_unseen_forces:_crook_of_unseen_forces,staff_of_cackling_wrath:_staff_of_cackling_wrath,staff_of_traps:_staff_of_traps,staff_of_many_rays:_staff_of_many_rays,staff_of_speaking:_staff_of_speaking,staff_of_mithral_might:_staff_of_mithral_might,staff_of_wings:_staff_of_wings,staff_of_defense:_staff_of_defense,staff_of_stoneweaving:_staff_of_stoneweaving,staff_of_the_planes:_staff_of_the_planes,staff_of_hungry_shadows:_staff_of_hungry_shadows,quiemas_branch:_quiemas_branch,dragon_staff:_dragon_staff,staff_of_slumber:_staff_of_slumber,staff_of_abjuration:_staff_of_abjuration,staff_of_conjuration:_staff_of_conjuration,staff_of_divination:_staff_of_divination,staff_of_enchantment:_staff_of_enchantment,staff_of_evocation:_staff_of_evocation,staff_of_illusion:_staff_of_illusion,staff_of_necromancy:_staff_of_necromancy,staff_of_transmutation:_staff_of_transmutation,staff_of_weather:_staff_of_weather,staff_of_earth_and_stone:_staff_of_earth_and_stone,staff_of_vision:_staff_of_vision,staff_of_waves:_staff_of_waves,staff_of_the_woodlands:_staff_of_the_woodlands,staff_of_life:_staff_of_life,staff_of_nethys:_staff_of_nethys,staff_of_one_hundred_hands:_staff_of_one_hundred_hands,vril_staff:_vril_staff,staff_of_passage:_staff_of_passage,staff_of_the_hierophant:_staff_of_the_hierophant,winters_reach:_winters_reach,staff_of_power:_staff_of_power,lasirros_staff:_lasi